# Branch History Tab

Three complementary views: **Commit Graph** (commit-centric), **Branch Tracking** (sync-centric), **Branch History** (time-centric — one horizontal lane per branch).

Answers: which branches diverged/stale, where pushed vs unpushed, multi-remote divergence. Signature viz: **ghost track** under diverged lanes (faded default-branch progression since LCA).

## Data flow

```
App (tab=history) → request-branch-history { dateRange }
  → extension.loadBranchHistory → getBranchLifecycles()
  → branch-history-data { lifecycles, defaultBranch, remoteMains, window }
  → BranchHistoryTab → execute-branch-action (on success: reload branches/remotes/history/commits)
```

Messages/types: `BranchLifecycle`, `BranchHistoryPayload`, loading scope `branch-history` in `src/shared/types.ts`.

## Git layer

| Helper | Notes |
|--------|-------|
| `resolveDefaultBranch` | `origin/HEAD` symbolic ref → `main` → `master` → first local |
| `resolveHistoryDateWindow` | `presetDays: null` (All) **capped at 90d** — unlike graph unbounded All |
| `getBranchLifecycles` | local lifecycles + remote-only (`!localBranchName` from `getRemoteBranches`) |
| `computePerRemoteDivergence` | per-remote `{remote}/{defaultBranch}...branch` behind counts |
| `sortBranchLifecycles` | default → diverged (severe→high→mild) → active → remote-only → merged |

`branch-status.ts`: `detectStatus`, `generateDescription`, `STALE_THRESHOLD_DAYS = 7`.

### Status algorithm

| Status | Condition |
|--------|-----------|
| merged | tip is ancestor of default branch (wins over stale) |
| diverged mild | ahead>0 and behind 1–5 |
| diverged high | behind 6–12 |
| diverged severe | behind 13+ |
| active | behind=0 |
| remote-only | no local `refs/heads/<name>` |

**Stale** = secondary flag when `daysSinceActivity > 7` on non-merged locals — not a primary status.

## Tab behavior

- Lazy load: `request-branch-history` only when `tab === "history"` (not in `loadInitialData`).
- Shared `dateRange` across tabs; switching tabs does **not** reset it.
- First visit: if range still default `7d`, promote to `30d` once (`getState()` flag).
- Default selection: checked-out → first diverged → default branch.
- `.current` = checked out; `.selected` = detail/quick-actions target.

