## SVG rules — DO

- Time flows left→right; default branch topmost with thicker bar.
- Hash labels at both bar ends; remote triangle flags only when `behindLocal > 0`.
- Ghost track for **all diverged local** branches only.
- Three-tier gridlines: daily subtle, weekly labeled, Today accent.
- Remote-only: dashed bar, `remoteColor`, opacity ~0.35, no ghost track.
- Theme via `useThemeColors()` / `--sg-history-*`; no hardcoded hex in components.

## SVG rules — DO NOT

- Cross-lane fork/merge connector curves between lanes.
- Ghost track for active, merged, or remote-only lanes.
- Remote markers when fully pushed (`behindLocal = 0`).
- Use `stale` as primary status.
- Invalid SVG attrs like `color-mix` — use `fillOpacity` / `strokeOpacity`.

## Light theme

`body.vscode-light`: darken `--sg-history-*` tokens for contrast. Selected lane labels: `--selection-fg` on `.branch-history-lane-label.selected`. Raise label/hash/LCA opacity in `GhostTrack` / `BranchLane`.

