| File | Role |
|------|------|
| `BranchHistoryTab.tsx` | Summary strip, legend, selection, detail |
| `TimelineSvg.tsx` | Grid + lane layout |
| `BranchLane.tsx` | Label, bar, dots, stale pill |
| `GhostTrack.tsx` | Diverged ghost + LCA connector |
| `RemoteMarker.tsx` | Triangle + unpushed bracket |
| `HistoryDetail.tsx` | Metrics, remote cards, quick actions |

Reuse graph `DateRangeBar` — do not duplicate under `history/`.

## Contextual actions

Same `execute-branch-action` as Tracking — always pass `branchName` + `remote`.

| Status | Primary |
|--------|---------|
| synced | — |
| ahead | Push N |
| behind | Pull N |
| diverged | Push + Pull |
| no-upstream | Set Upstream |
| remote-only | Create Local Branch |

**Out of scope v1:** rebase, PR, checkout, copy name, detail resize, cross-tab graph navigation.

